snippet.title: COD Modern Warfare II Multiplayer & Warzone 2.0 Official Reveal Trailer | COD Next Showcase 2022
snippet.description:
Get your first look at Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2's Warzone 2.0, as well as a look at multiplayer. Dive into the future of Call of Duty in this latest trailer that was showcased during the Call of Duty Next Showcase.

Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II releases on October 28, 2022. You can play the campaign a week early if you pre-order the game.

#cod #callofduty #gaming
